text: Diablo Pass (or Devil's Pass) is the deepest part of Laguna de Bay, with a depth of 20 meters. The pass is a marine channel located between Talim Island and the main landmass of the municipalities of Binangonan and Cardona in the province of Rizal. == References== ==Other websites== * Laguna Lake Development Authority (Official) * Diablo Pass, Province of Rizal * Diablo Pass, Geoview Category:Straits of the Philippines Category:Rizal
